  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-blind 52 to 104 Week Off-therapy Extension Study to Evaluate the Long Term Growth and Development of Pediatric Hypertensive Patients 6 - 17 Years of Age Previously Treated With Aliskiren in Studies CSPP100A2365 and/or CSPP100A2365E1</official_title>
