  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      52-104 week off-therapy second extension to study CSPP100A2365 to assess growth and
      development in pediatric hypertensive patients previously treated with aliskiren in studies
      SPP100A2365 and SPP100A2365E1
    </textblock>
